{"type":null,"faqId":10494,"title":"P6-U06   短信","answer":"<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t1.<span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">编辑短信时如何切换手写输入法</span> \n</h3>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">新建一封短信，点击输入框，下面弹出软键盘，默认为华为输入法，点击软键盘上方键盘图标，选择“全屏手写”或“半屏手写”输入方式。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31682\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"> </span>\n</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<span>2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">删除或者锁定同一个会话中的特定短信，批量删除</span> \n</h3>\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31683\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"> </span>\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">会话模式下，读信息界面，长按需要锁定的一条短信，选择锁定信息，便可以锁定该短信。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">信息界面，长按一条会话，选择需要删除的会话，按删除，从便可以删除该短信。</span><span></span> \n</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<span>3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">短信转发</span><span>/</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">群发与保存草稿方法，最多群发条数</span> \n</h3>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">短信转发：会话模式下，读信息界面，点击需要转发的某一条短信，选择转发，转发给指定联系人。</span> \n</p>\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31685\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">短信群发：新建一条短信，点击</span> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31686\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">进入添加联系人界面，选择需要添加的联系人，点击<b>确定</b>，群发短信到选择的联系人。</span> \n</p>\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"></span> \n<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">4.</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">长短信支持汉英字</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">数</span> \n</h3>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:黑体;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">长短信最多支持英文</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">1377</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">个，中文</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">607</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">个</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:黑体;\"> </span>\n</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">5.手机最多支持保存多少条短信</span> \n</h3>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">一个会话里边短信支持</span><span>500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">条或彩信</span><span>50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">条（用户可以在设置中修改）。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">对于手机总的短彩信条数没有限制，与手机剩余存储空间相关。</span> \n</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">6.如何设置短信中心</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">号码</span> \n</h3>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:黑体;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">HUAWEI\nP6-U06</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">不支持编辑短信中心号码。</span><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<br />\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"></span> \n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>","faqTypeId":136,"faqType":"信息与邮件","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1231","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-SMS-Email","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1397630260000,"seriesProductName":"EDGE-U00","visitedTimes":67,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}